INSERT INTO ForumEntries VALUES('VI0001', 2016, 1, 'P0000009I', '2016-07-19 06:36:38', 'A0000018D', '2018-12-07 13:29:25', 'I am thrilled I found this place! Dr. Brown and his staff are wonderful! Dr. Brown spent a lot of time on the examination and answered our many questions. I appreciated that he didn"t push any unnecessary services or products on us. He found a lump on one of our cats and told us just to monitor it and bring him back in if it gets any worse, rather than opting to run a bunch of expensive tests on him immediately. We brought our cat in about a month later to have the tests done and he was very upfront about the cost and what they were testing for. I also like that they send you an appointment reminder text the day before. Their prices are reasonable and the first exam is free. This is the only place I"ll be bringing my cats to from now on!');
INSERT INTO ForumEntries VALUES('VI0001', 2016, 1, 'P0000009I', '2016-07-19 06:36:38', 'A0000017T', '2017-11-16 01:40:44', 'Today we found a carpet we wanted and asked the sales guy to come over to price it out. It is an 8x10 and he gave the price, we agreed and then he went to write us up. When we went to pay, I noticed the price was different that the quote from 10 minutes ago by about $40. He said I needed to buy 8x12 instead because they don"t have a use for the other 2". Well, neither do I, this was not in the agreed upon price and it is a remnant so they can cut however they want.');
