INSERT INTO ForumEntries VALUES('NZ0003', 2017, 1, 'P0000009I', '2019-07-12 21:03:55', 'A0000025G', '2017-11-29 04:08:16', 'I was told so many great things about this place but my entire experience was awful. The food wasn"t very good, way too greasy. My fries were luke warm and my tray was literally covered in grease. I needed about 50 napkins and a shower after that. The service was pretty awful too. I can"t believe I paid $14 for a small meal with no extra fixings. On national cheeseburger day of all days too. Such a disappointment and I"ve never gone back since. Best thing about it was the soda, but that"s pretty difficult to mess up.');
INSERT INTO ForumEntries VALUES('NZ0003', 2017, 1, 'P0000009I', '2019-07-12 21:03:55', 'A0000007U', '2017-07-12 19:28:31', 'The food was really good, I highly recommend the ahi tuna appetizer, ravioli and the skirt steak!');
INSERT INTO ForumEntries VALUES('NZ0003', 2017, 1, 'P0000009I', '2019-07-12 21:03:55', 'A0000020T', '2018-11-30 01:53:35', 'Wow. So surprised at the one and two star reviews!  We started with the most tender calamari. Although the marinara sauce was a bit bland, but a touch of salt made it just right. My husband had the veal with peppers and said it was so delicious and tender. The mashed potatoes were perfect. I had the salmon Diablo which was also delicious. Our salad was beautiful! Dressing was served on the salad and it was a nice amount. We ended our delicious meal with a piece of tiramisu. Our server Matt was right on!! Very pleasant and knowledgeable about the menu. Our appetizer, salad and entrees were timed perfectly. I love salad and did not mind that my entree was served while I was still eating it! No problem it let my dinner cool to just the right temp for me to eat it comfortably.');
INSERT INTO ForumEntries VALUES('NZ0003', 2017, 1, 'P0000009I', '2017-11-18 04:02:14', 'A0000013E', '2019-11-15 01:12:02', 'I got stuck in Myrtle Beach last week and stayed here waiting for another flight.  Very clean, comfortable and right near the airport.  I would definitely stay again.');
