INSERT INTO ForumEntries VALUES('NZ0003', 2017, 1, 'P0000009I', '2018-12-25 10:14:57', 'A0000021Y', '2017-08-26 14:52:31', 'Never had Belizean food or have heard of them and they"re right in front of my building for 7 months. Finally made my way over there and it"s so dang good! Chicken fell off the bone. I ordered tamales since it"s the special right now and it"s huge for $5.50! Why did I wait so long! I was skeptical at first didn"t know what to expect. Owners are super nice.');
INSERT INTO ForumEntries VALUES('NZ0003', 2017, 1, 'P0000009I', '2018-12-25 10:14:57', 'A0000011F', '2017-01-24 13:43:40', 'Came here on a whim to try it out with my fiance and we were not impressed at all. Ordered the street corn queso and it was super lacking on flavor and also pulled a large chunk of butter from it. Tried to save it a little with the sauce tray and even added salsa to it and still wasn"t there. My Sonoran dog looked like it was from the previous day... typical dry wrinkled no snap day-old dog, the brioche bun was soggy from too much butter. And the tacos were cold. We Couldn"t even finish the meal. The salsa was the only highlight of the lunch. Also watched a server shatter a glass over the ice well and proceed to use the ice that the glass had broken into to serve a customer. I will NEVER return.');
INSERT INTO ForumEntries VALUES('NZ0003', 2017, 1, 'P0000009I', '2018-12-25 10:14:57', 'A0000021Y', '2019-05-18 13:34:32', 'I specifically go to this location even though it"s a bit far from me because of the friendly staff and great recommendations!');
INSERT INTO ForumEntries VALUES('NZ0003', 2017, 1, 'P0000009I', '2018-12-25 10:14:57', 'A0000019A', '2017-04-22 19:46:47', 'I"m never disappointed picking up a slice at Desert Ridge slices - the kids love  it, and I"m a fan of the NYC triangle slice too. Plus, I pick up all my weekly magazine reads in their shop as well.');
INSERT INTO ForumEntries VALUES('NZ0003', 2017, 1, 'P0000009I', '2018-12-25 10:14:57', 'A0000011F', '2019-03-25 07:07:28', 'Planning ahead is the way to go when it comes to Vegas, and while I don"t think you HAVE to use an outside VIP company to plan, I don"t really see a disadvantage to doing so.  I would definitely call Red Carpet VIP again.');
INSERT INTO ForumEntries VALUES('NZ0003', 2017, 1, 'P0000009I', '2018-12-25 10:14:57', 'A0000018D', '2016-04-07 12:34:24', 'It"s so popular that I didn"t try it until recently. The bubble tea here is really good. It"s pricier than the one in Rose tea, but you also get more.');
INSERT INTO ForumEntries VALUES('NZ0003', 2017, 1, 'P0000009I', '2018-12-25 10:14:57', 'A0000018D', '2017-01-11 07:43:06', 'Price wasn"t too bad...all you can eat wings for like $13.  I had the garlic parmesan which seemed a little bland.  Then I tried the Hot Wings...and it was kind of spicy....not too bad.  The ranch was a bit watery...');
INSERT INTO ForumEntries VALUES('NZ0003', 2017, 1, 'P0000009I', '2018-12-25 10:14:57', 'A0000030V', '2016-04-27 06:22:24', 'I went here today to upgrade to an iPhone X. They were awesome to work with. They mirrored everything from my current phone to the new one. That saved me so much time and aggravation if I had to do it. They were very knowledgeable and friendly! Highly recommend!');
