INSERT INTO ForumEntries VALUES('NZ0003', 2018, 2, 'P0000006T', '2016-02-16 00:58:11', 'A0000005P', '2018-10-22 21:47:43', 'The store manager Bras personally went out if his way to assist me in gathering all the materials I needed for my current project. He knows his store, bounced around to show me all options, and seemed to have recommendations on each project. This guy must love what he does because he knows everything in the store (or he is a constant do-it-yourselfer).');
INSERT INTO ForumEntries VALUES('NZ0003', 2018, 2, 'P0000006T', '2016-02-16 00:58:11', 'A0000005P', '2016-08-01 18:28:02', 'I considered giving this place 4 stars, because we went back a couple days later and the food was cold and missing that extra special love like we had the first time.  But it was a Friday evening and there was an Indian soap opera on the TV I think we interrupted....So, obviously, I can"t blame them.');
INSERT INTO ForumEntries VALUES('NZ0003', 2018, 2, 'P0000006T', '2016-02-16 00:58:11', 'A0000020T', '2016-08-21 11:42:48', 'Great food. Try the chop its huge.friendly service and down home atmosphere.');
INSERT INTO ForumEntries VALUES('NZ0003', 2018, 2, 'P0000006T', '2016-02-16 00:58:11', 'A0000016U', '2017-09-09 19:50:00', 'As a resident of Mountains Edge, its obvious we are missing the necessities....Trader Joe"s (I"ll even settle for a Sprouts), Costco or a NICE big gym...BUT what we do have is this place!!  Barking Dogs is the only place I buy my dog, Phoebe"s food and get her groomed. Phoebs is even on a first name basis in this local gem. Staff is very knowledgeable about all things DOGS!!  They love your baby as much as you love them. Its literally less than a mile from my casa.  Yes, my pup and I are lucky and even spoiled with its location.  Be jealous.  Be very jealous. ;)');
INSERT INTO ForumEntries VALUES('NZ0003', 2018, 2, 'P0000006T', '2016-02-16 00:58:11', 'A0000001Q', '2019-04-13 14:09:06', 'Place was okay...');
INSERT INTO ForumEntries VALUES('NZ0003', 2018, 2, 'P0000006T', '2016-02-16 00:58:11', 'A0000001Q', '2017-09-03 00:42:52', 'Even though I haven"t had much luck at this location over the years, I still stop by when I am at this mall. I"m still a longtime fan of the brand (since high school, mind you) and I am still optimistic.');
INSERT INTO ForumEntries VALUES('NZ0003', 2018, 2, 'P0000006T', '2016-02-16 00:58:11', 'A0000028N', '2017-07-27 21:56:28', 'We went to see England play in the Euro 2012 and it was fun! Everyone was totally into it.');
INSERT INTO ForumEntries VALUES('NZ0003', 2018, 2, 'P0000006T', '2016-02-16 00:58:11', 'A0000001Q', '2016-10-11 05:18:35', 'I had a glass of nice refreshing Greek white that hit the spot. The Greek Salad we had was super fresh and crunchy with a perfect dressing and just the right amount of feta.');
INSERT INTO ForumEntries VALUES('NZ0003', 2018, 2, 'P0000006T', '2016-02-16 00:58:11', 'A0000030V', '2018-02-05 09:05:49', 'This is always a must visit on vegas trips.  I"ve had the St. Louis crepe (ham and cheese) and Nutella (peanut butter and banana). Yumm this place is consistently delicious every time.  The 20 minute wait is worth it for these crepes, just try and find a table early on since the seating is shared with the caf next door. Seems a little pricey at about $10 but what isn"t pricey in Vegas?');
INSERT INTO ForumEntries VALUES('NZ0003', 2018, 2, 'P0000006T', '2016-02-16 00:58:11', 'A0000028N', '2016-10-06 18:58:34', 'Our regular plumber is great, but a little pricey, so we decided to try someone new.  Belsito"s rating on Yelp made us give them a try.  We called on a Saturday afternoon for a non-emergency.  They told us someone would call us back and let us know when they could come out.  About an hour later the doorbell rang and it was the plumber.  Luckily we were home as we never got a call.');
