INSERT INTO ForumEntries VALUES('FH0004', 2018, 1, 'P0000008O', '2017-06-19 17:20:07', 'A0000022F', '2017-01-11 00:28:10', 'Good, clean place to get a mani/ pedi. The two came to $39 with tax and they did a great job of both. TVs all over so you can watch tv and freindly staff.');
INSERT INTO ForumEntries VALUES('FH0004', 2018, 1, 'P0000008O', '2017-06-19 17:20:07', 'A0000005P', '2018-07-29 14:11:46', 'While I enjoyed the company of my friends, I would not come back to this restaurant, primarily because of the poor service. Once we were all seated, we were not greeted by anyone for over half an hour, and when someone did come by, we asked whether we could place our orders, to which he said he could not; he"s doing something else - so we waited at least another 15 minutes before someone came to finally take our orders.');
INSERT INTO ForumEntries VALUES('FH0004', 2018, 1, 'P0000008O', '2017-06-19 17:20:07', 'A0000008Z', '2017-04-05 15:24:09', 'Their specialty dishes are very unique.  The spicy tuna nachos are amazing. Some of my favorites are: lemon roll and the edamame is a must.  For desert also try the chocolate chip cookie with fudge and vanilla ice cream - yummy');
INSERT INTO ForumEntries VALUES('FH0004', 2018, 1, 'P0000008O', '2016-02-05 21:18:31', 'A0000002K', '2019-10-17 19:10:31', 'Yesterday they were my saving grace, when Papa John"s let me down SEVERELY.');
INSERT INTO ForumEntries VALUES('FH0004', 2018, 1, 'P0000008O', '2016-02-05 21:18:31', 'A0000012T', '2019-10-24 07:17:33', 'Don"t expect any fancy surroundings. It looks like a hole in the wall but you"ll be convinced to enter the door when you get a whiff of the food (which can be detected from a block away). The staff are very friendly although sometimes the service is slow. If you don"t like to wait, call ahead and take it home!');
INSERT INTO ForumEntries VALUES('FH0004', 2018, 1, 'P0000008O', '2016-02-05 21:18:31', 'A0000002K', '2018-11-06 18:04:49', 'The young man grating the cheese played with his smartphone typing out a few messages. Replaced it to his pocket and continued handling the cheese without washing his hands or using any plastic gloves.');
INSERT INTO ForumEntries VALUES('FH0004', 2018, 1, 'P0000008O', '2016-02-05 21:18:31', 'A0000010W', '2016-07-26 21:36:57', 'Go with "The Big Breakfast" for ~$12 if you"re hungry, and I"m telling you, you"d be pretty full by the end of it you wouldn"t want lunch!');
INSERT INTO ForumEntries VALUES('FH0004', 2018, 1, 'P0000008O', '2016-02-05 21:18:31', 'A0000021Y', '2018-09-04 06:03:57', 'Would possibly go back if in the neighborhood, more likely if a daily special was one that seemed exciting. I"m not near Matt"s and there was nothing here that made it worth the drive.');
INSERT INTO ForumEntries VALUES('FH0004', 2018, 1, 'P0000008O', '2016-02-05 21:18:31', 'A0000010W', '2017-01-29 07:23:17', 'This is my very first bike! JT was very helpful along with his staff! Very friendly and they really take their time to help you and find what you need! I was there for a really long time but i never got the feeling that i was an annoyance. They really take go out of their way to make sure you get all the answers to make an informed decision. Nonetheless, I would highly recommend coming here!');
INSERT INTO ForumEntries VALUES('FH0004', 2018, 1, 'P0000008O', '2016-02-05 21:18:31', 'A0000021Y', '2017-05-23 10:04:17', 'Out of all the places in Las Vegas to pick for Cinco de Mayo food, drinks, and music, we picked this one based on YELP reviews.  We were first time visitors.  We will definitely return very soon!');
