INSERT INTO ForumEntries VALUES('JX0006', 2019, 1, 'P0000005Y', '2019-09-27 01:00:41', 'A0000019A', '2016-01-11 00:58:05', 'It"s been about two weeks since Omar did my window tint. It looks great, he had to scrap off old nasty window tint that started to bubble. The work they do is awesome, this is the 3rd vehicle he has done for me. I"ve been very happy every time. I"ll for sure always keep my business with him. Prices are fair, but the quality and professional service speaks for itself.  Thanks Omar');
INSERT INTO ForumEntries VALUES('JX0006', 2019, 1, 'P0000005Y', '2019-09-27 01:00:41', 'A0000024F', '2019-12-06 20:18:31', 'Every member of the staff is extremely friendly and courteous. No matter what time of day I am there everyone is (or pretends to be) in the best mood ever. Very professional, very clean and modern, even relaxing!');
INSERT INTO ForumEntries VALUES('JX0006', 2019, 1, 'P0000005Y', '2019-09-27 01:00:41', 'A0000019A', '2016-06-08 23:57:08', 'I am thrilled I found this place! Dr. Brown and his staff are wonderful! Dr. Brown spent a lot of time on the examination and answered our many questions. I appreciated that he didn"t push any unnecessary services or products on us. He found a lump on one of our cats and told us just to monitor it and bring him back in if it gets any worse, rather than opting to run a bunch of expensive tests on him immediately. We brought our cat in about a month later to have the tests done and he was very upfront about the cost and what they were testing for. I also like that they send you an appointment reminder text the day before. Their prices are reasonable and the first exam is free. This is the only place I"ll be bringing my cats to from now on!');
INSERT INTO ForumEntries VALUES('JX0006', 2019, 1, 'P0000005Y', '2019-09-27 01:00:41', 'A0000019A', '2017-08-08 06:22:53', 'Love this place! It"s simple. It"s priced fair and the waffle was very good. Sunday was my day to say I have had enough of the twigs and berries and I want pancakes! Well at least a waffle although they have big banner that states now serving pancakes but really who goes to a Waffle Cafe for pancakes...the name tells you what their specialty is.');
