INSERT INTO ForumEntries VALUES('BD0007', 2016, 1, 'P0000005Y', '2017-12-13 15:58:11', 'A0000001Q', '2017-02-04 20:55:18', 'I had the LA wrap and my wife had more soup. Both were really good. They make fresh, homemade soup every day.');
INSERT INTO ForumEntries VALUES('BD0007', 2016, 1, 'P0000005Y', '2017-12-13 15:58:11', 'A0000018D', '2018-03-13 17:46:00', 'They were nice enough to comp our burgers and asked if we wanted new ones. We were good with that. They also said they would give us free dessert. OKAAAAY!!!');
INSERT INTO ForumEntries VALUES('BD0007', 2016, 1, 'P0000005Y', '2017-12-13 15:58:11', 'A0000018D', '2018-06-09 20:24:34', 'Tried hamburger steak and it was so delicious. Gravy/sauce they put on the hamburger steak was perfect! Also came with onion rings on top which I love. Chicken katsu was amazing! Chicken katsu here is crunchy and surprisingly has a flavor by itself that you really don"t need a sauce for it. Best chicken katsu I had.');
INSERT INTO ForumEntries VALUES('BD0007', 2016, 1, 'P0000005Y', '2017-12-13 15:58:11', 'A0000024F', '2019-02-24 16:17:06', 'Came to this place based on yelp reviews and it did not disappoint. Got the chicken wings to start, kao soi with chicken and an dish from the chefs special - Steamed fish coconut curry. Chicken wings were good, especially when hot, the sauce gelatinized as it cooled. Kao soi was the best I"ve ever had, an excellent portion ans the chicken was very tender. The the fish coconut curry was good too, wasn"t much of a curry but was still very flavourful. Service was fast and people were so friendly and kind. Will definitely go back to try other menu items.');
INSERT INTO ForumEntries VALUES('BD0007', 2016, 1, 'P0000005Y', '2017-12-13 15:58:11', 'A0000001Q', '2018-06-16 23:08:32', 'Out of all the places in Las Vegas to pick for Cinco de Mayo food, drinks, and music, we picked this one based on YELP reviews.  We were first time visitors.  We will definitely return very soon!');
INSERT INTO ForumEntries VALUES('BD0007', 2016, 1, 'P0000005Y', '2017-12-13 15:58:11', 'A0000001Q', '2016-08-15 20:34:12', 'I most definitely would recommend this place to anyone. Thanx to cake world my cake for my son"s baby shower made the entire event that much better! I will be going back in the future!');
