INSERT INTO ForumEntries VALUES('BD0007', 2017, 1, 'P0000001A', '2016-08-01 15:56:37', 'A0000013E', '2019-10-25 04:42:07', 'For my hard lens it took time to get that correct as well, but that is expected. It also took me several times asking my Oakland optometrist to get my records faxed to them. McCauley-Celin at first said they never received them, but they then found them in another computer system. When the first lens didn"t fit quite right I went to the Wexford office to get it checked and left my lens there as it needed to be returned. When my new lens came they asked for my old one and apparently it was lost out there or somewhere. I paid for my lens with my FSA account but then was told that it should be covered under my insurance and that they would take care of it. That didn"t happen so I called to ask about it. They never got back to me so I went to their Gibsonia office and they said that they owed me money and it was fixed. This all again took several months.');
INSERT INTO ForumEntries VALUES('BD0007', 2017, 1, 'P0000001A', '2016-08-01 15:56:37', 'A0000010W', '2019-02-08 20:48:38', 'Great lunch today. Staff was very helpful in assisting with selections and knowledgeable on the ingredients. We enjoyed the BBQ chicken with tika masala sauce and really good naan bread. The biryani with chicken was also yummy! Fun to see the food being prepared in the tandoori ovens. Great addition to the fast casual scene in Cleveland.');
