INSERT INTO ForumEntries VALUES('PA0008', 2016, 2, 'P0000006T', '2019-02-15 23:03:54', 'A0000017T', '2017-06-23 18:46:52', '2 mini starters, 2 entrees (tapas style) shared + 1 desert with one glass of wine gave us a $90 bill and we left without feeling full. The desert was a caramel fondant with pear ice cream, probably the only thing we ate that was so incredible we would have paid twice the price for. Otherwise it was too pricy.');
INSERT INTO ForumEntries VALUES('PA0008', 2016, 2, 'P0000006T', '2019-02-15 23:03:54', 'A0000025G', '2019-11-17 19:41:57', 'Perfect Grilled Cheese was amazing and worth a repeat  visit.  Chicken club lacked unique flavor and was average.  The BLT was great with the bread making the sandwiches.  Now for the sides: tomato soup was delicious and a perfect complement to the grilled cheese.  Shoe string fries were great, nothing not to like about them and the green pea salad in peanut sauce was delicious.  We will definitely return for another try!');
INSERT INTO ForumEntries VALUES('PA0008', 2016, 2, 'P0000006T', '2019-02-15 23:03:54', 'A0000022F', '2016-12-20 07:12:07', 'One thing that concerned me was the gal cooking the burgers had long hair that was not tied back.  Just an FYI in case you"re squeamish about plucking hair out of your food.');
