INSERT INTO ForumEntries VALUES('PA0008', 2019, 2, 'P0000003N', '2017-07-03 04:57:39', 'A0000013E', '2018-06-02 09:09:13', 'Entry: Got my entire group on a guestlist with a 1:1 (guy/girl) comp until midnight. Sign up on their website and you will get a text back if you have been put on. The entry line was confusing as hell, with at least 4 different lines (staff, promoter, general, VIP). There was an open bar for ladies from 11-12 so things were a bit rushed. This came back to bite me in the ass as I made the mistake of leaving my guestlist line for the shorter staff entry line. Members of my group were with this female staff member who said could get us all free in even though our guy:girl ratio had more guys. I spoke with her personally to make sure of it before I left my line. Well...SHE LIED! The bouncers upfront simply took the first equal ratio of guys:girls, leaving me and another guy stuck paying $40 entry. My girlfriend was not pleased with the fact that one of my other group members (who came stag) got in for free and I didn"t. Whatever, lesson learned. Don"t rush in. Don"t be tempted by an open bar or a shorter line. Stick with guestlist if you"re approved. Make sure your group ratio is even or favors girls. Don"t listen to otherwise!');
INSERT INTO ForumEntries VALUES('PA0008', 2019, 2, 'P0000003N', '2017-07-03 04:57:39', 'A0000018D', '2017-03-11 11:56:56', 'Everything we ordered was completely disgusting. We ordered from the late night menu, I got the veggie fajitas beans and rice. They left out my tortillas in my Togo order the beans and rice were disgusting. My best friend ordered the fish tacos which ended up being some sort of strange shredded fish. My boyfriend got the salmon salad, which was ok but would"ve been better but the salmon was dry. They left out my garlic fries and on top of all of this disgusting food it was 91$!!! I will never eat here ever again');
