INSERT INTO ForumEntries VALUES('BW0009', 2016, 1, 'P0000008O', '2017-11-28 09:06:52', 'A0000004V', '2016-01-31 01:29:09', 'Without a doubt,  my favorite Indian restaurant to date. There is a lot of variety, but my favorite dish is the chicken korma. The butter chicken is also fantastic. It is deliciously sweet and kid-friendly because it is not too spicy. For those of you who like to feel the burn, they have plenty of options to choose from, as well. I recommend the Thali for people who are just starting to explore their Asian culinary senses. Also, if you are a naan connoisseur, you need add Palais d"Ajit to your list.');
INSERT INTO ForumEntries VALUES('BW0009', 2016, 1, 'P0000008O', '2017-11-28 09:06:52', 'A0000012T', '2016-12-28 01:15:24', 'Just fulfilled a bucket list item and got my nose pierced!! This shop is beautiful!! So clean!! The staff is super friendly. I was nervous but the piercer calmed me down with his sense of humor. Great place!!! It"s so nice to have a quality shop on the Westside.');
INSERT INTO ForumEntries VALUES('BW0009', 2016, 1, 'P0000008O', '2017-11-28 09:06:52', 'A0000012T', '2017-03-13 16:28:38', 'When Petal first opened I was taken aback by the open, airy space but also by the prices. At first blush, this store didn"t offer much under $150-$200 besides accessories. Yet, over time, Petal has begun to bring in a more varied selection that appeals to a wider, stylish market. While they still offer the $300-$450 cocktail dresses, they also showcase a variety of merchandise in the $75-$100 range. Plus, if you can catch them on a sale day, it"s worth a trip.');
