INSERT INTO ForumEntries VALUES('JS0010', 2017, 2, 'P0000003N', '2016-02-23 21:00:09', 'A0000020T', '2018-02-02 10:19:34', 'We start hitting balls and our waiter shows up.  He literally walks us through the entire menu, page by page, explaining burgers, and appetizers, and frozen margaritas like we had never been to a pub before and didn"t know what a "slider" was.  (Mind you, you pay by the hour at this place, so someone taking your time is quite annoying).  We order a bucket of beer and chips and guac, and shoo him off and get back to our golf.  Beers arrive, chips arrive - and our waiter arrives..... and stays.... and gets all chatty about football and where my family is from, and his Grandma in Colorado, and what it was like working after Christmas, and all sorts of topics that none of us care to talk about.  ugh, leave us alone - we are here for golf and beer, not a new pal.');
INSERT INTO ForumEntries VALUES('JS0010', 2017, 2, 'P0000003N', '2016-02-23 21:00:09', 'A0000029I', '2016-04-01 11:36:59', 'As for the food itself, I"d call it "decent". The donuts were delicious, but the chocolate mousse-like dip it came with was rather tasteless. Actually, I actively didn"t like the chocolate dip and I LOVE chocolate. My duck scramble was good but nothing special. I loved the potatoes, but everything else just...normal.');
INSERT INTO ForumEntries VALUES('JS0010', 2017, 2, 'P0000003N', '2016-02-23 21:00:09', 'A0000003O', '2016-05-06 07:25:49', 'Just found out about this secret treasure!  Love this studio and the staff!!!! I haven"t practiced yoga in a studio for a while, but this place is very welcoming to Yogi"s of all levels! I love power flow with Shannon- she"s got a great energy and inspires me to challenge myself! Love love love this studio! If you are going for the first time, park off Glenway by the bank- its easier to find! :)');
INSERT INTO ForumEntries VALUES('JS0010', 2017, 2, 'P0000003N', '2016-02-23 21:00:09', 'A0000012T', '2019-12-12 01:59:12', 'I ordered the Mediterranean and it had a lot of flavor from all the different veggies and spices. My only complaint is: the crust was a bit dry, a little more olive oil wouldn"t have hurt.');
INSERT INTO ForumEntries VALUES('JS0010', 2017, 2, 'P0000003N', '2016-02-23 21:00:09', 'A0000014A', '2019-07-19 23:00:00', 'Had the occasion over the last few weeks to experience their sports medicine/physical therapy department.  Outstanding.  Drs. Anthony "Tony" Walker and Jennifer Hannon are a great team.  They really know their stuff.');
INSERT INTO ForumEntries VALUES('JS0010', 2017, 2, 'P0000003N', '2016-02-23 21:00:09', 'A0000003O', '2018-05-25 17:21:28', '(and make sure to read the non-PC T-shirts while you wait - funny!)');
INSERT INTO ForumEntries VALUES('JS0010', 2017, 2, 'P0000003N', '2016-02-23 21:00:09', 'A0000014A', '2017-11-28 10:08:06', 'I also saw other items on the menu like fish balls, chicken wings, shaved ice. My friend got a mango drink with fresh mango in it!');
INSERT INTO ForumEntries VALUES('JS0010', 2017, 2, 'P0000003N', '2016-02-23 21:00:09', 'A0000022F', '2017-07-30 01:36:11', 'This is my second visit; my first was back during CES in Jan. with a young friend visiting Vegas for the first time and who had never had a bloody mary...');
